  "description": "In spawn_autonomous_daemon_run() (runtime_daemon.rs:254), the daemon subprocess is spawned with stdout/stderr/stdin all piped to Stdio::null(). Change this to redirect stderr to a log file at ~/.ao/<scope>/daemon/daemon.log. Implement basic log rotation (e.g. rename old log on startup if over 10MB). This is critical for debugging daemon crashes — currently any panic or error is silently lost. Also add structured startup/shutdown log lines with timestamps.",
